                <h1>Comprehensive CBC Background Check Guide</h1>
                <p>A CBC background check, or Criminal Background Check, is a process that verifies an individual's criminal history, helping employers assess potential hires' trustworthiness. This check can reveal felony and misdemeanor charges, ensuring a safer workplace. It's essential for roles involving vulnerable populations or sensitive information.</p>
